question: Match the following:
column_II: Transfer of sperms into female genital tract
Fusion of male and female gametes
Attachment of blastocyst to uterine wall
matches: Insemination–Transfer of sperms into female genital tract
Fertilisation–Fusion of male and female gametes
Implantation–Attachment of blastocyst to uterine wall
answer: Gametogenesis–Formation of gametes (sperms/ovum), Insemination–Transfer of sperms into female genital tract, Fertilisation–Fusion of male and female gametes, Implantation–Attachment of blastocyst to uterine wall
